---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Ghana Business Analysis: Economic Reports, Sector Intelligence, Risk Assessments"
  description="In-depth Ghana business analysis for investors and diaspora founders. Sector rankings, risk alerts, policy tracking, and opportunity scoring. Updated continuously."
  keywords="Ghana economic analysis, Ghana business report, Ghana investment analysis, Ghana sector report 2026, Ghana risk assessment, diaspora investment guide"
>
  <div class="hero hero--bg hero--analysis">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-label">Evidence-Grounded</div>
      <h1>Ghana Business Analysis</h1>
      <p>Ground-truth reporting powered by GhanaWorld v3.0. 25 agents, real-time web research, no hype.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="section reveal">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-label">Published</div>
        <div class="section-title">Reports</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card-grid">
        <a href="/analysis/gse-crash-2026" class="article-card">
          <span class="card-tag risk">Risk Alert</span>
          <h3>GSE Crash: From 15,000 to 12,990 in One Week</h3>
          <p>The Ghana Stock Exchange hit a record 15,185 then lost 14% in days. T-bill compression, search-for-yield exhaustion, thin market structure, and the cocoa question. Four scenarios with indicator watchlist.</p>
          <div class="card-meta">
            <span>March 29, 2026</span>
            <span>Capital Markets</span>
            <span>8 min read</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/analysis/hormuz-crisis-ghana-2026" class="article-card">
          <span class="card-tag risk">Risk Alert</span>
          <h3>Hormuz Crisis: How $114 Oil Reaches a Ghanaian Market Stall</h3>
          <p>Diesel up 25.7% in one NPA window. Four transmission channels traced with real pricing data. Sector-by-sector impact. What to watch next.</p>
          <div class="card-meta">
            <span>March 28, 2026</span>
            <span>Macro and Global</span>
            <span>12 min read</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section reveal">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-label">In Development</div>
        <div class="section-title">Pipeline</div>
        <div class="section-desc">Articles advancing through the 8-stage publishing pipeline with 3 mandatory quality gates.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card-grid">
        <div class="article-card" style="opacity:0.65;">
          <span class="card-tag policy">Policy Analysis</span>
          <h3>BoG Rate Cut to 14%: What the Split Vote Means</h3>
          <p>The 3-1-1 vote reveals the tension between easing and Hormuz risk. May MPC is the critical decision point.</p>
          <div class="card-meta">
            <span class="status-badge">Stage 1 of 8</span>
            <span>Monetary Policy</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="article-card" style="opacity:0.65;">
          <span class="card-tag scenario">Scenario Analysis</span>
          <h3>Ghana's Triple Shock: Three Scenarios for 2026</h3>
          <p>Hormuz, cocoa, and GSE hit simultaneously. Base case, upside, downside, and wildcard with probability estimates.</p>
          <div class="card-meta">
            <span class="status-badge">Stage 1 of 8</span>
            <span>Macro Scenario</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
